# ============================================================
# Google sisselogimine, registreerimine ja Drive pilve salvestus
# ============================================================
# Täpsem juhend: docs/GOOGLE-SETUP.md
#
# 1. Google Cloud Console: https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 2. Luba API-d: Google Drive API, Google Picker API (APIs & Services → Library).
# 3. OAuth consent screen (kui veel pole): APIs & Services → OAuth consent screen.
# 4. Loo OAuth 2.0 Client ID: Credentials → Create Credentials → OAuth client ID
#    - Application type: Web application
#    - Authorized JavaScript origins: http://127.0.0.1:5197 ja tootmise URL (nt https://noodi-meister-vol1.vercel.app)
# 5. Kopeeri Client ID siia alla ja käivita: npm run dev
# ============================================================
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=

# ============================================================
# Microsoft sisselogimine + registreerimine (MSAL) ja OneDrive (Graph)
# ============================================================
# Azure / Entra: App registrations → sinu rakendus
#   - Authentication → platvorm: Single-page application (SPA), MITTE Mobile and desktop
#   - Redirect URI-d peavad TÄPSELT klappima getMicrosoftRedirectUri():
#       origin + Vite BASE_URL (vaikimisi base: '/') → lõpus kaldkriips, nt:
#       https://noodimeister.ee/
#       https://www.noodimeister.ee/
#       http://127.0.0.1:5197/
#     (Lisa nii www kui ilma, kui mõlemad domeenid kasutusel; dev port = vite.config server.port)
#   - Verceli preview URL (iga haru) vajab eraldi URI-d, kui testid OAuth'i seal.
# API permissions (Microsoft Graph, Delegated): User.Read, Files.ReadWrite; Grant admin consent.
#
VITE_MICROSOFT_CLIENT_ID=
# Tenant authority segment:
#   common          — Entra (kõik org-id) + isiklikud Microsofti kontod (sobib signInAudience AzureADandPersonalMicrosoftAccount)
#   organizations   — ainult töö-/koolikontod (sobib AzureADMultipleOrgs)
#   <tenant-guid>   — ainult üks kataloog
VITE_MICROSOFT_TENANT_ID=common
# ============================================================

# ============================================================
# Kohaliku e-post+parool: parooli taastamine (Vercel API + KV + Resend)
# ============================================================
# Vercel: sama KV mis Stripe/admin (KV_REST_API_URL, KV_REST_API_TOKEN).
# RESEND_API_KEY — https://resend.com (domain kinnitatud saatjaga).
# RESEND_FROM — nt "Noodimeister <noreply@noodimeister.ee>"
# NM_PUBLIC_SITE_URL — taastamislingi baas (nt https://noodimeister.ee), ilma lõpus /
#
# RESEND_API_KEY=
# RESEND_FROM=
# NM_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://noodimeister.ee
#
# Kohalik dev (vite): proxy /api → tootmine või `vercel dev`
# NM_DEV_API_PROXY=https://noodimeister.ee
# ============================================================

# ============================================================
# Toetuse automatiseerimine (Stripe) – vt docs/TOETUS-STRIPE-AUTOMAATIKA.md
# Backend (Vercel API): lisa Vercel Project → Settings → Environment Variables:
#   STRIPE_SECRET_KEY, STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET, KV_REST_API_URL, KV_REST_API_TOKEN (Vercel KV)
# Frontend (vajadusel): kui API on teisel domeenil, siis VITE_API_BASE=https://sinu-api.vercel.app
# ============================================================
# VITE_API_BASE=

# ============================================================
# Administraator: toetus e-arvega / organisatsioonidele (vt docs/TOETUS-ARVE-ADMIN.md)
# Vercel: ADMIN_EMAILS = sinu e-mail (või komadega mitu), ADMIN_SECRET = salajane võti (esialgse parooli seadistamiseks ja API jaoks)
# Leht: noodimeister.ee/administraator (peidetud, menüüs linki pole)
# ============================================================
# ADMIN_EMAILS=info@la-stravaganza.com
# ADMIN_SECRET=
